---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
import { site } from "../data/site";
---

<BaseLayout title="联系方式 | WangAo-0" description="WangAo-0 的邮箱、微信、资助入口和自媒体视频平台链接。">
  <section class="page-shell">
    <div class="page-heading">
      <p class="eyebrow">Contact</p>
      <h1>联系方式</h1>
      <p>这里先保留公开联系入口。邮箱和微信支付打赏已可用；微信号和自媒体主页没有放真实信息前，先用待补充状态标记。</p>
    </div>

    <div class="contact-grid refined-contact">
      <article class="media-card contact-primary">
        <p class="card-kicker">Email</p>
        <h3>邮箱</h3>
        <p>{site.email}</p>
        <a class="button primary" href={`mailto:${site.email}`}>发送邮件</a>
      </article>

      <article class="media-card pending-card">
        <p class="card-kicker">WeChat</p>
        <h3>微信</h3>
        <p>可以放微信号，或替换为真实二维码图片。</p>
        <span>待补充</span>
      </article>

      <article class="media-card sponsor-card">
        <p class="card-kicker">Sponsor</p>
        <h3>微信支付打赏</h3>
        <img class="qr real-qr" src="/media/sponsor-qr.jpg" alt="微信支付打赏二维码" />
        <p>如果文章或项目对你有帮助，可以用这个二维码支持一下。</p>
      </article>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="section-heading">
      <p class="eyebrow">Video</p>
      <h2>自媒体视频平台</h2>
      <p>这里适合放 Bilibili、YouTube、小红书或知识视频主页。真实主页确定后，只需要更新站点数据。</p>
    </div>
    <div class="grid-3">
      {site.mediaLinks.map((link) => (
        <article class="card link-card">
          <p class="card-kicker">Video Channel</p>
          <h3>{link.label}</h3>
          <p>{link.note}</p>
          {link.href === "#" ? <span class="status-pill">待补充链接</span> : <a class="text-link" href={link.href}>访问平台</a>}
        </article>
      ))}
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
